OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774390292
OL,3,CInfluencers rave over full-fat Jersey
OL,4,Cand Guernsey milk amid sales surge
OL,6,FInfluencers and nutritionists are
OL,7,Fcelebrating the benefits of drinking
OL,8,Ffull-fat Jersey and Guernsey milk,
OL,9,Famid a spike in sales across the
OL,10,FBritish Isles.
OL,12,FChannel Island dairies are not allowed
OL,13,Fto export it to the UK, but herds of
OL,14,Fcows are kept there and many people
OL,15,Fcannot seem to get enough.
OL,17,FUK sales for one brand of full-fat
OL,18,FJersey milk at Ocado have increased by
OL,19,Falmost 230% in the last two years.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
