FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774390292
OL,3,CInfluencers rave over full-fat Jersey
OL,4,Cand Guernsey milk amid sales surge
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Tesco sold more than three
OL,7,Fmillion extra litres of Jersey milk in
OL,8,F2025 ` a rise of more than 100%.
OL,10,FSunna van Kampen, better known by his
OL,11,Fhandle @tonichealth, which has more
OL,12,Fthan 1.7 million followers across
OL,13,Fsocial media, is one of many online
OL,14,Finfluencers encouraging his followers
OL,15,Fto buy whole milk from the Bailiwicks.
OL,17,FHe says: "It's so much more creamy,
OL,18,Fthick and delicious.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774390292
OL,3,CInfluencers rave over full-fat Jersey
OL,4,Cand Guernsey milk amid sales surge
OL,6,F"Five years ago, everyone was moving
OL,7,Faway from dairy products and into
OL,8,Fplant-based alternatives, which are
OL,9,Foften ultra-processed.
OL,11,F"Now, retailers are constantly telling
OL,12,Fme the sales of cottage cheese, Greek
OL,13,Fyoghurt and Jersey milk are through
OL,14,Fthe roof, so I think people are going
OL,15,Fback to the basic, traditional things
OL,16,Fwe always consumed."
OL,18,FNutritionists like Kit Chamier have
OL,19,Falso been quick to point out the
OL,20,Fhealth benefits of drinking milk from
OL,21,Fthe Channel Islands.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774390292
OL,3,CInfluencers rave over full-fat Jersey
OL,4,Cand Guernsey milk amid sales surge
OL,6,FHe explains: "Jersey and Guernsey milk
OL,7,Fis much more nutritious than UK milk,
OL,8,Fand we've got slightly higher protein
OL,9,Flevels.
OL,11,F"The nutritional content of milk
OL,12,Fdoesn't change based on its fat
OL,13,Fprofile, so the protein, calcium and
OL,14,Fvitamin levels don't change between
OL,15,Fskimmed and whole milk.
OL,17,F"But I think people are moving away
OL,18,Ffrom the low-fat everything trend."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774390292
OL,3,CInfluencers rave over full-fat Jersey
OL,4,Cand Guernsey milk amid sales surge
OL,6,FJersey Dairy has reported a 20%
OL,7,Fincrease in full-fat milk sales over
OL,8,Feach of the last five years, with the
OL,9,Fproduct rising from 5% to 11% of the
OL,10,Fcompany's total sales.
OL,12,FEamon Fenlon, Managing Director of
OL,13,FJersey Dairy, says: "It seems to be
OL,14,Fpredominantly young people who are
OL,15,Flooking for good sources of natural
OL,16,Fprotein, and Jersey milk is high in
OL,17,Fprotein.
OL,19,F"Jersey cows are a totally different
OL,20,Fbreed, they're very efficient at
OL,21,Fturning grass into nutrient-rich milk.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774390292
OL,3,CInfluencers rave over full-fat Jersey
OL,4,Cand Guernsey milk amid sales surge
OL,6,F"We ship to Hong Kong, where full-fat
OL,7,Fmilk makes up 60% of our sales, and to
OL,8,FKorea, where they only want the gold
OL,9,Ftop (full-fat milk)."
OL,11,FIt is not just Jersey; Guernsey Dairy
OL,12,Ffull-fat milk sales have also soared.
OL,14,FThe company has seen a 30% boost in
OL,15,Fwhole milk purchases since 2019,
OL,16,Fdespite a decline across other
OL,17,Fproducts.
OL,26,@qD@EpmqD@Spn
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1774390292
OL,3,CInfluencers rave over full-fat Jersey
OL,4,Cand Guernsey milk amid sales surge
OL,6,FAndrew Tabel, Managing Director at
OL,7,FGuernsey Milk, adds: "Lots of people
OL,8,Fcome here from all over the world,
OL,9,Ftaste our low-fat milk and think it's
OL,10,Ffull-fat - so when they taste our
OL,11,Fwhole milk, they think it's even
OL,12,Fbetter.
OL,14,F"It's a luxury, but at 5% it's still
OL,15,Fclassed as a low-fat food.
OL,17,F"I think people are more aware of
OL,18,Fwhere their food comes from, and
OL,19,Fkeeping it as fullsome as possible."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
